Title: When adding a new site all sites are marked as dirty
Component: wato
Class: nastiness
State: done
Date: 2012-10-26 12:43:07
Targetversion: 1.2.2

When adding a new site or changing the configuration of a site, all sites are
marked as dirty. It would be better to only mark the master site (currently
editing on) and the modified site as dirty.

